description.en: YFI CREDITS is an open-source Decentralized protocol which enables you to easily access YFI CREDITS DUAL STAKING, FARMING, GOVERNANCE VOTE, LENDING and BORROWING DeFi Services from a simple dashboard. Our goal is to simplify the process of lending and borrowing of crypto assets while maintaining Decentralization and transparency by Leveraging the superior capability (i.e., high performance and smart contract functionality).
